         Measure Anything, Measure Everything 

                 
             
                Posted by  Ian Malpass   on February 15, 2011             
                     

         If Engineering at Etsy has a religion, it’s the Church of Graphs. If it moves, we track it. Sometimes we’ll draw a graph of something that isn’t moving yet, just in case it